            "byte_start": 2313718,
            "byte_stop": 2321763,
            "stop": 561.218,
            "text_blocks": [
              {
                "stop": 561.218,
                "text": "I take it the strike has long -- as since over.",
                "byte_stop": 2321763,
                "byte_start": 2313718,
                "start": 559.212
              }
            ],
            "start": 559.212
          },
          {
            "speaker": {
              "roles": null,
              "view_count": 0,
              "href": "https://api.oyez.org/people/harry_r_sachse",
              "name": "Harry R. Sachse",
              "last_name": "Sachse",
              "length_of_service": 0,
              "thumbnail": null,
              "ID": 28145,
              "identifier": "harry_r_sachse"
            },
            "byte_start": 2321763,
            "byte_stop": 3059043,
            "stop": 745.55,
            "text_blocks": [
              {
                "stop": 568.613,
                "text": "The strike lasted about 11 months and it’s over.",
                "byte_stop": 2351334,
                "byte_start": 2321763,
                "start": 561.218
              },
              {
                "stop": 597.092,
                "text": "On the statutory base, I want to say first that the President, Sec -- through delegation, Secretary of Interior and Director of Bureau of Indian Affairs have very broad authority under 25 U.S.C. 2 and 25 U.S.C. 9 to make such rules and regulations and decisions as are necessary in this area.",
                "byte_stop": 2465228,
                "byte_start": 2351334,
                "start": 568.613
              },
              {
                "stop": 608.613,
                "text": "But the Act that we’re primarily concerned with here is the Snyder Act which was passed in 1922.",
                "byte_stop": 2511308,
                "byte_start": 2465228,
                "start": 597.092
              },
              {
                "stop": 613.188,
                "text": "And I think the Act is clear on its face.",
                "byte_stop": 2529593,
                "byte_start": 2511308,
                "start": 608.613
              },
              {
                "stop": 629.41,
                "text": "It’s the Authorization Act of Bureau of Indian Affairs to provide health, education, welfare and all sorts of other services to Indians wherever they live in the country.",
                "byte_stop": 2594482,
                "byte_start": 2529593,
                "start": 613.188
              },
              {
                "stop": 637.907,
                "text": "We don’t say that this Act prohibits the Bureau of Indian Affairs from doing things for Indians off reservations.",
                "byte_stop": 2628441,
                "byte_start": 2594482,
                "start": 629.41
              },
              {
                "stop": 655.345,
                "text": "But I think it’s quite clear that the Act simply is the Authorization Act as it created no programs and legislative history is clear on this too that to solve points of order that there was no authorization for the Bureau of Indian Affairs, Congress passed this particular act.",
                "byte_stop": 2698240,
                "byte_start": 2628441,
                "start": 637.907
              },
              {
                "stop": 661.868,
                "text": "I won’t burden the Court with going through what I’ve done in detail in the brief there.",
                "byte_stop": 2724362,
                "byte_start": 2698240,
                "start": 655.345
              },
              {
                "stop": 662.916,
                "text": "The language of it is clear.",
                "byte_stop": 2728542,
                "byte_start": 2724362,
                "start": 661.868
              },
              {
                "stop": 682.265,
                "text": "The Bureau of Indian Affairs under the supervision of the Secretary of the Interior shall direct, supervise and expend such moneys as Congress may from time to time, appropriate, for the benefit, care, and assistance of the Indians throughout the United States for the following purposes: General support civilization, including education.",
                "byte_stop": 2805864,
                "byte_start": 2728542,
                "start": 662.916
              },
              {
                "stop": 692.027,
                "text": "At the time this Act was passed there was no general support program, financial support program neither on or off Indian reservations or in the country as a whole.",
                "byte_stop": 2844944,
                "byte_start": 2805864,
                "start": 682.265
              },
              {
                "stop": 698.913,
                "text": "Social Legislation of 1930s hadn’t been passed at that time.",
                "byte_stop": 2872529,
                "byte_start": 2844944,
                "start": 692.027
              },
              {
                "stop": 702.985,
                "text": "I thought it's a hard question.",
                "byte_stop": 2888829,
                "byte_start": 2872529,
                "start": 698.913
              },
              {
                "stop": 725.385,
                "text": "I think that the respondents are really reaching to take the language in that Act and to say that it commands the Secretary of the Interior, institute a welfare program and that that Welfare program must be for Indians both on and off the reservations.",
                "byte_stop": 2978377,
                "byte_start": 2888829,
                "start": 702.985
              },
              {
                "stop": 739.697,
                "text": "And one, I would say certainly neutral observer of this Act, Mr. Wolf who at one point, I think had some role in representing the respondents in this case.",
                "byte_stop": 3035638,
                "byte_start": 2978377,
                "start": 725.385
              },
              {
                "stop": 745.55,
                "text": "He's written a very good law review article on this subject and that --",
                "byte_stop": 3059043,
                "byte_start": 3035638,
                "start": 739.697
              }
            ],
            "start": 561.218
          },
          {
            "speaker": {
              "roles": [
                {
                  "institution_name": "Supreme Court of the United States",
                  "date_start": -16570800,
